### 3.6 Get registrations for non-existent event
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/events/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006/registrations
Authorization: Bearer {{$auth.token("EventsRegistration")}}
Accept: {{halContentType}}

> {%
